msgid "Project Lifetime"
msgstr ""

msgid "The period during which the system will be in operation. Components whose lifetime is below that of the project lifetime must be replaced during operation, which will be taken into account in the cost calculation. In addition, the residual value of the components is determined at the end of the project lifetime."
